IZIMANGA ezigilwe yisilomo somgadli weBafana Bafana, uPercy "Young-Lion" Tau, zizokhukhumeza umqeqeshi weqembu lesizwe nozakwabo balo mdlali ukuthi bangakubanga ukushisa kwi-2019 Africa Cup of Nations (Afcon) ese-Egypt kusuka ngoJuni 21 kuya kuJulayi 19.UTau, obolekiswe yiBrighton & Hove Albion yase-England kwiRoyal Union Saint Gilloise (RUSG), ngoMsombuluko ebusuku uqokwe njengomdlali ovelele eligini yaseBelgium - iProximus League Player of Year.#IRetweetWhatILike
