May 6, 2019Bekuyisizini yakhe yokuqala utau edlala ngaphandle kwaseNingizimu Afrika, nakhona ashiye ngonyaka owedlule edle umklomelo ofanayo - i-2018 PSL Footballer of the Season.Ungene embangweni walo mklomelo enamagoli angu-11 nangu-13 awakhile kanti kwabebanga nabo kubalwa uFaiz Selemani waseComoros noNikola Strom.Kungenzeka ukuthi labo abebanga nabo lo mklomelo uTau ubamboze ngempelasonto enza into yamehlo esiza iRUSG ibuya ku 2-0 ize inqoba umdlalo.Ungene kwimpelasonto edlule eseqokiwe embangweni.Emdlalweni wangempelasonto ungene ngesiwombe sesibili belandela ngemuva ngo 1-0 kwiCrcle Brugge, eshaye elesibili ngemuva kwemizuzwana.Umdlalo nokho uphele ezikaTau zihamba phambili ngo 3-2 ngemuva kokuba inxele laseMalahleni liphake iphasi evalelwe nguYoussouf Niakite ngaphambi kokushaya elalo lokuwina.Uhlabana nje ngoMsombuluko usenamagoli ayishiyagalombili nangu-11 awakhile.Ngokwe-website yeRUSG, uSelemani ulale isithathu kwathi uNiakite waphuma isine ngemuva kukaTau.Kwi-Afcon, Ibafana iqhathwe kwiGroup D neMorocco, Ivory Coast nomkhaya beCosafa, iNamibia.UTau ubeyisibani esiholele iBafana kwi-Afcon kwazise emidlalweni yokuhlunga ubalwa nabadlali abashaye amagoli amaningi.Kube amagoli akhe amabili iBafana ehlule ngawo iLibya ukuze iwelele e-Egypt.

BAHLUKENE phakathi abalandeli baZodwa Wabantu ezinkundleni zokuxhumana ngenkulumo yakhe ngabathandana nabobulili obufanayo.UZodwa Wabantu uziqhathe nabanye babalandeli bakhe ngemuva kokubonakala ohlelweni lwakhe ethi yena akancintisani nabesilisa abathandana nabobulili obufanayo ngoba yena unenanazi bona abanayo. ngenxa yale nkulumo ayenza esiqeshini sakamuva. NgoLwesibili abaseka uZodwa nabo baqale owabo umkhankaso ezinkundleni zokuxhuma okhuthaza ukuthi lungavalwa lolu hlelo oluvela kuMoka Love. Twitter, Inc: Save Zodwa Wabantu's Show on Moja Love TV - Sign the Petition! 
