July 9, 2019Ofake le petition uthe igama lohlelo lukaZodwa lilodwa nje likubeka kucace ukuthi lunezinto okungenzeka zingehli kahle kwabanye, yingakho libizwa nge 'uncensored'. Abanye abalandeli bakhe ezinkundleni zokuxhumana bamuvikele bethi empeleni ukhuluma iqiniso uZodwa, 'akushoyo ubengakusho ngenzondo.'Ohlelweni uZodwa uzwakale ethi: "Inkinga yezitabane ukuthi bazitshela ukuthi banenanazi, kodwa banomphambili. Thina sinenanazi. Siyabemukela nje ukuze uma sifaka imikhiqizo yokuziphaqula nabo bayifake noma futhi sixoxa ngamadoda nabo baxoxe," kusho uZodwa.Ethintwa yiSolezwe ngalolu daba uZodwa ukugcizelelile ukuthi inkulumo yakhe ubeyibhekise kumngani wakhe othandana nabobulili obubodwa owamebela izimpahla zakhe. Unxuse abantu ukuthi babuke uhlelo lwakhe bayeke ukuphawula ngezinto ezenzeka empilweni yakhe.

ZINENGWE ukungafiki kwezikhulu zikahulumeni izifundiswa ezimashele ukuhlala isikhathi eside zingasebenzi ngoLwesithathu, eThekwini. Bekungokwesithathu lezi zifundiswa zibhikisha zikhala ngokuhlala emakhaya nezitifiketi. Ngesikhathi zimasha zizokwethula incwadi yezikhalo, zikhale ngokungabibikho kwezikhulu ezivela eMkhandlwini weTheku noma kuhulumeni ukuzolalela izikhalo zazo. UMnuz Nkulululeko Ndlovu, ongomunye walaba ophothule izifundo zakhe ze-Accounting ngo-2016, uthe isiqala ukubanenga indaba yokuzitshwa abaholi. “Lokhu kuzoholela ekutheni sigcine sesenza izinto ngenye indlela. Asibona abantu abanodlame ngoba siyizifundiswa, kodwa ukungathathelwa kodaba lwethu phezulu kusenza sibone ukuthi abakugqizi qakala esizokhala ngakho. Okwesithathu manje simasha kungafiki sikhulu ukuzosamukela.” kusho yena. Uqhube wathi ngesikhathi bethweswa iziqu zemfundo ephakeme abaholi abakuhulumeni babebashayela ihlombe kodwa uma sebengawutholi umsebenzi abasabonwa nangokhalo. “Sifuna ukwazi ukuthi uhulumeni nezinkampani benzani ukulungisa lesi simo,” usho kanje. ‘Angilona ivila, anginawo umsebenzi’ - Londiwe Khuzwayo (24) oyingxenye yezifundiswa ezibhikishayo namhlanje eThekwini zikhalaza ngokungaqashwa. 
