August 22, 2018Umeluleki weMeya yeTheku, uMnuz Mlungisi Ntombela, uthe bazithathela phezulu izikhalo zezifundiswa ezingasebenzi kodwa akuwona umkhandlu kuphela okumele uphendule ngokuntula kwamathuba omsebenzi. “Esikwenzile njengomkhandlu sixhumane nehhovisi likaNdunankulu sacela ukuthi sike sithole usuku lapho bonke ongqongqoshe beminyango KwaZulu-Natal bezoza bezochaza kabanzi ngezinhlelo zokuqasha intsha. Inkinga enkulu esibhekene nayo njengamanje ukuthi abantu abaqashwa emnyangweni kahulumeni ngoba imali ayikho. Ngisho abaneziqu zokufundisa abazithola ngemifundaze yoMnyango wezeMfundo nabo bahlezi emakhaya,” kuchaza yena.  Ekhuluma ePhalamende lapho abephendula khona imibuzo umengameli wezwe, uMnuz Cyril Ramaphosa, uthe uhulumeni kuningi asekwenzile ukuzama ukwehlisa inkinga yokungabibikho kwamathuba omsebenzi. “Enye yezinto ezokwandisa amathuba omsebenzi kuleli abatshalizimali, sidinga ukhukhulisa umnotho wethu ukuze kuzoba namabhizinisi azoqasha abantu. Ngo-Okthoba nonyaka sizoba nengqungquthela yabatshalizimali,” kusho uRamaphosa.

SESINYUKELE ku-7 572 isibalo sabantu osekuqinisekisiwe ukuthi bahaqwe yigciwane iCovid-19 kuleli, kanti isibalo sababulawe yileli gciwane sinyukele ku-148. Lokhu kuqinisekiswe nguNgqongqoshe wezeMpilo kuleli uDkt Zweli Mkhize ngoLwesibili ebusuku. Isibalo sabahaqekile sinyuke ngo-352 kanti esabashonile sinyuke ngabalishumi uma kuqhathaniswa nezibalo ezimenyezelwe ngoMsombuluko. Sebebalelwa ngaphezulu kuka-268 000 abantu asebehlolelwe iCorona kuleli kanti abawu-10 000 kubo bahlolwe kumahora awu-24 edlule.%%%twitter https://twitter.com/hashtag/COVID19?src=hash&ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#COVID19Statistics in South Africa as at 05 May 2020. 
pic.twitter.com/I2476c7kDe— Dr Zweli Mkhize (@DrZweliMkhize)EWestern Cape isibalo sabahaqekile sesifinyelele ku-3 609, eGauteng bawu-1 697 kanti KwaZulu-Natal bawu-1 142 abahaqekile. IWestern Cape iphinde ibe nesibalo esiphezulu sabashonile kunazo zonke ezinye izifundazwe kanti izolo kumenyezelwe ukuthi kwabayishumi abashonile, abayisikhombisa abakulesi sifundazwe. Kuzokhathaza abaningi ukunyuka kwesibalo sabantu abathelelekayo ngosuku njengoba sekweqe u-300 ezinsukwini ezimbalwa ezidlule. Kusukela ngoMeyi 1 kuya ku-Meyi 5 isibalo sabantu abahaqekile kuleli sinyuke ngo-1 925. NgoMeyi 1 izwe lingene esigabeni sesine sikathaqa okuhambisana nokuxegiswa kweminye yemithetho ebekiwe. Uhulumeni ubeke eminye imithetho ukuqinisekisa ukuphepha kwabantu, njengokuphoqwa kwabantu ukuthi bafake izifonyo ngaso sonke isikhathi uma besemphakathini. Nezinkampani zibekelwe umgomo wokuthi ziqinisekise ukuthi zihlinzeka abasebenzi ngezifonyo kuphinde kube khona nezibulali magciwane endaweni yokusebenza. Izolo umengameli Cyril Ramaphosa uhambele isifundazwe iKZN ukuzohlola ukuthi isifundazwe siqhuba kanjani empini yokulwa naleli gciwane. Uveze ukuthi uhlabeke umxhwele ngomsebenzi owenziwa yisifundazwe kulandela ukuvakashela isibhedlela esisha iDr Pixley Ka Isaka Seme Hospital athe sizosiza kakhulu empini naleli gciwane njengoba ososayensi beveze ukuthi lisazosabalala ngamandla kuleli. %%%twitter https://twitter.com/hashtag/COVID19?src=hash&ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#COVID19
