INKAMPANI enkulu yezindiza yaseNigeria i-Air Peace isizibophezele ukuthutha abantu bakuleliya lizwe abaseNingizimu Afrika ibabuyisele eNigeria mahhala.Leli galelo livezwe esitatimendeni esikhishwe nguNgqongqoshe wezokuXhumana namaZwe oMhlaba waseNigeria uMnuz Geoffrey Onyeama ngeledlule.Kulesi sitatimende u-Onyeama uveza ukuthi umnikazi we-Air Peace uMnuz Allen Onyema unikele ngalokhu ukuze kwelekelelwe abantu baseNigeria abakuleli ngethuba lokubuyela ezweni labo.Ungqongqoshe uthe leli thuba lilandela izigameko zodlame nokwebiwa kwempahla ezitolo zabantu bokufika ezisabalale ezindaweni ezahlukene esifundazweni iGauteng emasontweni amabili edlule.Kulezi zigameko bangaphezu kuka-10 abantu abashonile kanti babalelwa kwabangu-400 ababoshiwe mayelana nokudala udlame nokweba emphakathini."Ngakho umphakathi uyanxuswa ukuthi wazise izihlobo eziseNingizimu Afrika ezingathanda ukulisebenzisa leli thuba. Abantu abadabuka eNigeria bayanxuswa ukuba bathinte ihhovisi leKhomishini ePhakeme esePitoli noma bathinte iConsolate General yaseNigeria eseGoli," kusho okhulumela ungqongqoshe uMnuz Ferdinand Nwonye esitatimendeni.Leli galelo elithathwe yi-Air Peace lenze abantu bakuleli babeka imibono yabo enkundleni yokuxhumana uTwitter.South Africa, the Proprietor of Air Peace Airlines Chief Allen Onyema, has volunteered to send an aircraft from Friday, 6th September 2019 to evacuate Nigerians who wish to return to Nigeria free of charge.%%%twitter https://twitter.com/hashtag/XenophobicAttack?src=hash&ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#XenophobicAttack
